com.percussion.services.publisher
Interface IPSEditionTaskLog

public interface IPSEditionTaskLog

This represents a single running of a single edition task. As each task is run, the data is recorded in these records.

Author:
dougrand

Method Detail

getReferenceId

long getReferenceId()
The reference id is a unique value generated for each task and each item published. The reference id will not recycle within any reasonable time period.

Returns:
the referenceId, may be null for a new object that hasn't been initialized.
